2. Filled in the required Last Name field with 'Doe'
3. Filled in the required Email field with 'john.doe123@example.com' (after fixing the duplicate email issue)
4. Set the Date of Birth to '01/15/1980'
5. Clicked the 'Save Customer' button

Looking at the current page state, I don't see any error messages, which suggests the customer was successfully created. The goal was specifically to add a customer with a specific date of birth, which I've accomplished.

Since the task has been completed successfully, I should inform the user that I've added the customer with the specified date of birth.
